title: GD Wardens
body:
Hey everyone,

We had a ton of applicants (54 wew) and many interviews that happened last week. It is now time to announce your new Wardens who will be moderating as well as being the voice of this community. 

Congratulations to those who have been selected and give them a warm welcome!

**Wardens:**

* Boggybuntu
* Tundra Fizz
* Jikker
* Evangele
* Mounting Dread
